repository-code: "https://github.com/mrdulasolutions/dreamagent"
url: "https://github.com/mrdulasolutions/dreamagent"
abstract: >-
  DreamAgent is a system and methodology for consolidating AI agent memories
  captured during the day into the weights of a small language model via
  nightly LoRA fine-tuning. By replacing retrieval-based memory with
  parametric memory, the trained "memory specialist" model acts as a
  knowledge oracle that any larger frontier agent can query — preserving
  privacy, reducing latency, and enabling cross-memory reasoning that
  vector retrieval cannot. The methodology includes a structured MemoryItem
  schema, a catastrophic-forgetting–aware rehearsal mix composer, an
  eval-gated promote/rollback pipeline, and a per-model tuning playbook.
